<div class="floatnone"><a href="/wiki/File:Han_Civilisation.png" class="image" title="Location of Han"><img alt="Location of Han" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/32/Han_Civilisation.png/250px-Han_Civilisation.png" width="250" height="185" border="0" /></a></div>
</div>
<small>The <strong class="selflink">Han Dynasty</strong> in 2 CE (brown), with military garrisons (yellow dot), dependent states (green dot), and <a href="/wiki/List_of_tributaries_of_imperial_China" title="List of tributaries of imperial China" class="mw-redirect">tributary vassal states</a> (orange dot) as far as the <a href="/wiki/Tarim_Basin" title="Tarim Basin">Tarim Basin</a> in <a href="/wiki/Western_Regions" title="Western Regions">the western</a> part of <a href="/wiki/Central_Asia" title="Central Asia">Central Asia</a></small></td>
