<div class="NavContent" style="border-style: none; padding: 0px; background-color:transparent; font-size: 95%; text-align: center; display:none; border-top: 0px solid #BEBEBE;">
<p><a href="/wiki/Chinese_historiography" title="Chinese historiography">Chinese historiography</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Timeline_of_Chinese_history" title="Timeline of Chinese history">Timeline of Chinese history</a><br />
